01:23:38,485 --> 01:23:40,180
Matt?

730
01:23:41,789 --> 01:23:43,916
Matt?

731
01:23:44,258 --> 01:23:45,987
Matt.

732
01:24:00,941 --> 01:24:01,965
Come over. Come here.

733
01:24:04,378 --> 01:24:06,209
We're gonna play
hide-and-seek now, okay?

734
01:24:06,413 --> 01:24:08,040
Okay, go.

735
01:24:11,318 --> 01:24:13,809
- We have to get out of here. Come on.
- What's going on?

736
01:24:14,021 --> 01:24:15,784
We have to go. We have to...

737
01:24:16,323 --> 01:24:17,881
Matt. Matt, no.

738
01:24:18,092 --> 01:24:19,286
Matt, no. No.

739
01:24:26,233 --> 01:24:27,894
- Get out.
- Matt.

740
01:24:28,102 --> 01:24:29,797
Get out.

741
01:24:30,003 --> 01:24:32,801
Matt. No. Matt.

742
01:24:33,006 --> 01:24:35,702
Get out. Whatever you do,
do not let them put out the fire.

743
01:24:35,909 --> 01:24:37,809
- What about you?
- I'm already dead.

744
01:24:39,413 --> 01:24:42,712
- Matt, come out. Matt.
- Matt.

745
01:24:46,019 --> 01:24:47,782
We'll find him.

746
01:29:03,176 --> 01:29:05,406
Mom. Dad.

747
01:29:06,380 --> 01:29:07,347
Where's Matt?

748
01:29:07,547 --> 01:29:09,742
- He's inside.
- I don't understand.

749
01:29:09,950 --> 01:29:12,578
- I thought you said it was over.
- Matt's trying to end it.

750
01:29:12,786 --> 01:29:13,810
- I gotta get in.
- Ma'am.

751
01:29:14,021 --> 01:29:17,013
No, you gotta let me in there.
I have to get my son.

752
01:29:17,224 --> 01:29:20,125
- Fire.
- Please let me go. Please.

753
01:29:20,327 --> 01:29:22,158
To unbind the spirits.

754
01:29:46,520 --> 01:29:48,385
What are we waiting for? Come on!

755
01:29:48,588 --> 01:29:50,317
Matt!

756
01:30:03,670 --> 01:30:05,695
Oh, my God.

757
01:30:06,273 --> 01:30:08,241
Okay.

758
01:30:11,211 --> 01:30:12,872
All right.

759
01:30:13,880 --> 01:30:17,372
I'm here. I'm here.

760
01:30:41,408 --> 01:30:42,932
The Lord is my shepherd.

761
01:30:43,143 --> 01:30:44,770
I shall not want.

762
01:30:45,011 --> 01:30:47,445
He maketh me
to lie down in green pastures.

763
01:30:48,348 --> 01:30:50,714
He leadeth me beside the still waters.

764
01:30:51,551 --> 01:30:53,849
He restoreth my soul.

765
01:30:54,054 --> 01:30:56,284
He leadeth me
in the path of righteousness.

766
01:31:01,461 --> 01:31:03,725
He helped my son.

767
01:31:28,121 --> 01:31:32,683
We're here. We're here. We're here.

768
01:31:46,907 --> 01:31:48,602
Matt.

769
01:31:54,614 --> 01:31:56,411
Be careful.

770
01:31:58,819 --> 01:32:00,343
Come on, wake up.

771
