01:32:18,538 --> 01:32:20,335
Wake up.

775
01:32:32,686 --> 01:32:35,382
Come on, Matty.
Come on, Matty, breathe.

776
01:32:37,624 --> 01:32:39,683
I love you.

777
01:32:52,005 --> 01:32:54,098
Wake up, Matt.

778
01:32:58,712 --> 01:33:00,543
I just love you so much.

779
01:33:03,016 --> 01:33:04,574
Come on, Matty, wake up.

780
01:33:05,518 --> 01:33:08,248
Please, come on, honey.

781
01:33:09,756 --> 01:33:11,314
Come on.

782
01:33:17,397 --> 01:33:19,524
You'll be all right.

783
01:33:37,050 --> 01:33:38,540
Hey.

784
01:33:49,429 --> 01:33:51,454
He's okay.

785
01:34:10,317 --> 01:34:13,946
I don't really care
if anybody believes me or not.

786
01:34:14,788 --> 01:34:17,018
I know what happened.

787
01:34:17,223 --> 01:34:22,217
Doctors and nurses know
and my family knows.

788
01:34:24,030 --> 01:34:27,056
And my son is alive...

789
01:34:28,368 --> 01:34:30,359
... and well.

790
01:34:31,338 --> 01:34:33,465
That's all that matters.

791
01:34:34,808 --> 01:34:38,039
They say that God works
in mysterious ways.

792
01:34:39,045 --> 01:34:42,811
They just don't always tell you
how mysterious those ways can be.

793
01:34:44,017 --> 01:34:46,110
Consider yourself warned.

